data.title: Survey: Name the Celebrities that share you Zodiac sign?
data.text:
I'm a Sagittarius and my birthday is December 18th. I only know a few celebrities from the top of my head that I share a birthday with.

Brad Pitt

Katie Holmes

Steven Spielberg

Christina A. (The singer)

I'm sure there are more but these are the only ones I know by heart.

I'm a Scorpio too and I'm going to add different ones then what you had. :]

Julia Roberts, Bill Gates, Owen Wilson, Ciara, Ryan Gosling, Brittany Murphy, Anne Hathaway, Matthew McConaughey, Nadine Velazquez, Fabolous, Jibbs and Analeigh Tipton.
